    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="Description">Description</h2><p><a href="https://cloudtraining.on.fleek.co">https://cloudtraining.on.fleek.co</a> is a static site hosted on IPFS using the <a href="http://Fleek.co">Fleek.co</a> platform.<sup class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn1" id="fnref1">[1]</a></sup></p><p>The source code is privately held on my GitLab server.</p><p>The static html is generated locally in my Development Environment and then directly uploaded to IPFS and deployed to fleek’s CDNs using the fleek cli-tool.</p><h2 id="Purpose">Purpose</h2><p>To Quickly and easily publish educational articles related to Cloud Technologies.</p><h2 id="Sources">Sources</h2><hr class="footnotes-sep"><section class="footnotes"><ol class="footnotes-list"><li id="fn1" class="footnote-item"><p><a href="https://fleek.co/">fleek.co</a> <a href="#fnref1" class="footnote-backref">↩︎</a></p></li></ol></section>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
